              "content": "<p> See the Qur’ān: 2:30-39; 3:33, 59; 4:1; 5:27-31; 7:11-27, 172-173, 189-190; 15:26-44; 17:61-65, 70; 18:50; 19:58; 20:115-126; 21:37; 23:12-13; 38:67-88; 49:13; 55:14). </p>",
              "sectionId": "book-one-god-s-messenger-adam-adam-satan-s-fall"
